description:
Dans talks about if there should be a national champion in college football. Dan talks about Dabo Swinney who said this years champion is no less than any other year. Dan says that with the SEC, ACC, and the Big12 you pretty much have 3 of the 4 final championship conferences in tact all except Ohio St. and the Big10.
